Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.45,Base,,0,0,0,,I have superpowers and\Ncan read your mind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Can I say something to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't walk down\Nthe kabuki {\i1}hanamichi {\i0}anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.61,Base,,0,0,0,,...we can walk down\Nthe Kouka silver bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.43,Base,,0,0,0,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:32.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:54.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Everyone dreams of becoming a superstar at least once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So that you can make the world envious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}1, 2, 3, quick like Allegro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Hold that hand and come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:09.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's build a rainbow together at Andante
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:15.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}You aren't anyone yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:20.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So any of your future can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:26.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Your dream is just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:31.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Little by little, you can become yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:37.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Tomorrow's gonna blow another wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:41.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So dream as many times as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:46.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Someday, become the stage's sparkling star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:51.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}so that the spotlight shines upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:04.24,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kaoru's Summer"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kaoru's Summer"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.98,Base,,0,0,0,,The students at the Kouka School\Nof Musical and Theatrical Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:10.42,Base,,0,0,0,,return to campus, refreshed from\Ntheir summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:14.54,Base,,0,0,0,,and began to ready themselves\Nfor a new semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.09,Base,,0,0,0,,It's so much hotter down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.05,Base,,0,0,0,,You guys went up north to Hokkaido, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, summers there are super cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I saw two of the Spring Troupe's shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:28.09,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to say, Ryuu Asahina's performance\Nin the final show was transcendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Hoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.52,Base,,0,0,0,,You cut your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.80,Base,,0,0,0,,It was hot long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.97,Base,,0,0,0,,You've got such great hair,\Nso of course it'd look good short!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:46.83,Base,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do {\i0}want to be an {\i1}otoko-yaku{\i0},\Nso I figured now's the time to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.87,Base,,0,0,0,,You're so cool! You look so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.74,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, guys, literally everyone\Ncuts their hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.04,Base,,0,0,0,,She's embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Kaoru's embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.30,Base,,0,0,0,,You're totally embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Whatever! What the hell is\Nwrong with you and Naracchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:05.25,Base,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you to\Nstart acting like pros!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Pros don't let themselves\Nget suntanned like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.14,Base,,0,0,0,,What kind of reaction is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.84,Base,,0,0,0,,And don't act like you're\Nnot in trouble, too, Naracchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:21.35,Base,,0,0,0,,I was just having so much fun,\NI didn't realize I was getting tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:26.85,Base,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter! Fine Kouka ladies\Ndo {\i1}not {\i0}let themselves get a tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Eek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Kaoru {\i1}does {\i0}go all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:40.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Why does Hoshino always\Nwalk around with an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.92,Base,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.01,Base,,0,0,0,,A teacher told her to lose the umbrella,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.93,Base,,0,0,0,,but she argued there's\Nno school rule against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Apparently she wants to be an actress or\Nsomething? So she doesn't want to get tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:04:00.02,Base,,0,0,0,,So then I posted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.40,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shin-Nase\Nfor Zushi Station"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.18,Base,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}didn't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:08.49,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, look over there.\NHe's on our baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:12.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'know, he's related to\Nthat hot major leaguer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? He's like, not even hot though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.83,Base,,0,0,0,,You think we'll finally\Nmake it to Koshien this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.32,Base,,0,0,0,,Ugh, look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.59,Base,,0,0,0,,A school uniform {\i1}and {\i0}an umbrella?\NWho does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, she went to my middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Apparently she wants to go to\Nthe Kouka theater school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.57,Base,,0,0,0,,but she still hasn't gotten in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.56,Base,,0,0,0,,We live near the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:54.83,Base,,0,0,0,,The sun shines bright, especially during\Nthese hot summer months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.17,Base,,0,0,0,,I can do what I can\Nto keep from getting tan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.74,Base,,0,0,0,,but there's not much I can do\Nabout the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:11.30,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shizuka Hoshino"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.18,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're\Nfeeling better, Mari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.87,Base,,0,0,0,,I was so scared when I heard\Nyou were in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.09,Base,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.42,Base,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:21.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru-chan! How nice of you to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:26.44,Base,,0,0,0,,My grandmother was a top {\i1}musume-yaku{\i0}\Nof the Kouka Acting Troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.57,Base,,0,0,0,,They called her\N"Spring's Lovely Snow White."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Even now, she's still surrounded by fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.63,Base,,0,0,0,,My goodness, is this her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, my granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! It's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.88,Base,,0,0,0,,She's a senior in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.92,Base,,0,0,0,,Is she? Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:48.18,Base,,0,0,0,,She must be breaking from tradition and\Nwon't be joining the Kouka troupe, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:54.14,Base,,0,0,0,,This is her last year to apply, so she's\Ngiving it all she's got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.14,Base,,0,0,0,,My, is that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.92,Base,,0,0,0,,We're rooting for you, hon! Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Your kidney stone surgery\Nmust have been so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Though with how you sparkle,\NI'm sure they pulled out a diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:12.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Everyone must be so disappointed.\NAfter all, I hardly look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Semester's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's hit karaoke on the way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.00,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm going on a date with my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.04,Base,,0,0,0,,What are you up to, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.38,Base,,0,0,0,,I've got lessons every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Kaoru's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I want to be an {\i1}otoko-yaku{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.81,Base,,0,0,0,,A cool, handsome actress\Nwho plays male roles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.02,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Yukiko Hoshino"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was in the middle of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Could you stop by the hospital\Non your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Grandma mentioned a book\Nshe wanted us to pick up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.68,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.17,Base,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:17.10,Base,,0,0,0,,I heard some girls the other day say you\Nwere trying out for some acting troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.93,Base,,0,0,0,,And, uh, my grandma's\Na big fan of that troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:23.45,Base,,0,0,0,,so she told me to ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Like... what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.61,Base,,0,0,0,,Ugh, what am I even saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.54,Base,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you Tsuji-san from South High?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Good luck in the Koshien prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:47.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Also, could you give this\Nto your brother Kaito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.68,Base,,0,0,0,,I really, really like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Whenever I feel down, I just watch\Nhim play, and it makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.72,Base,,0,0,0,,I know he's headed off\Nto the major leagues,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.43,Base,,0,0,0,,and he's engaged\Nto that model, Seira-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.91,Base,,0,0,0,,but I'd really appreciate it\Nif you'd give him my letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.76,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't want any part in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm not my brother's keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.90,Base,,0,0,0,,B-But--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.16,Base,,0,0,0,,The school {\i1}and {\i0}my brother\Ndon't want people doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.60,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.35,Base,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:38.12,Base,,0,0,0,,That's my name.\NKaoru Hoshino. What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Rikuto Tsuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.31,Base,,0,0,0,,The Kouka School of\NMusical and Theatrical Arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.48,Base,,0,0,0,,What do they teach you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.85,Base,,0,0,0,,Everything from proper manners\Nto singing and ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.04,Base,,0,0,0,,We do a {\i1}lot {\i0}of physical training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:56.52,Base,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:09:00.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Right? I gotta be able to lift\Nthose {\i1}musume-yaku {\i0}girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.77,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musume {\i0}what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:06.15,Base,,0,0,0,,The troupe's all-female, so they sort\Nactresses into male or female roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna have to wear a moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:14.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The guys in my class\Nmake fun of that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:18.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't mean to\Nmake fun of it! I was just surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.88,Base,,0,0,0,,I've seen your brother on TV a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:31.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Yeah, figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.14,Base,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.01,Base,,0,0,0,,My mom and grandma\Nwere both in the Kouka troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.50,Base,,0,0,0,,and my grandma was pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how\Nwe have that in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Rikuto's on the South High\NVarsity Baseball Team,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:58.58,Base,,0,0,0,,and every year, they make it to\Nat least the Koshien prelim finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.92,Base,,0,0,0,,But Rikuto usually ends up\Nwarming the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Tsuji's gotten a hell of\Na lot better all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:09.30,Base,,0,0,0,,He's got the skill, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.80,Base,,0,0,0,,He just gets into his head too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, come eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Here! I made this one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:26.56,Base,,0,0,0,,We're graduating this year, so you better\Nmake it to Koshien this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:30.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Good point. Not like I'll\Nget to play, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:34.82,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon! Your brother's going to\Nthe major leagues! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I never get bothered when\Npeople try to compare me to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause we're related doesn't mean\Nwe're the same! I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.59,Base,,0,0,0,,You're so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.24,Base,,0,0,0,,You have a hard time\Nexpressing yourself when you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Give it more feeling and\Nenunciate those syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.47,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You'll be a great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Your mother and grandmother\Nwere both great singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.83,Base,,0,0,0,,That's what I keep telling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:22.05,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Falling from the sky ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:27.39,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Like white snow, but warm, ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:33.77,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Like a spring fairy ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:38.44,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Fluttering down ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:47.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"When are you visiting your grandma next?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:52.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.71,Base,,0,0,0,,The sun's really bright today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, you've gotta\Nwatch out for that, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.29,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm super tan, like Othello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.52,Base,,0,0,0,,In the center of the Kouka stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.56,Base,,0,0,0,,there's this part of the apron\Ncalled the silver bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:17.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Only a few stars get to walk across it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.63,Base,,0,0,0,,The big stars, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.45,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be a top {\i1}otoko-yaku{\i0}\Nand walk across that silver bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:29.87,Base,,0,0,0,,You know those people who {\i1}say {\i0}"I'm getting\Nin!" when there's no guarantee they will,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.54,Base,,0,0,0,,then end up getting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.58,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.34,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll be honest, I wish I had their guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:41.42,Base,,0,0,0,,I could never say that. I know better than\Nanyone just how hard it is to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.16,Base,,0,0,0,,When are you going to\Nsee your grandma again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.46,Base,,0,0,0,,You sure have been coming to see me a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.46,Base,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.15,Base,,0,0,0,,How many guys are on a baseball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Nine. You hear the English number\Nused a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.57,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.35,Base,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do {\i0}spend all your time taking lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.55,Base,,0,0,0,,I can't come to watch,\Nbut I hope you guys win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.63,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll have to wear more manly fashions\Nwhen I get into the troupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.67,Base,,0,0,0,,so I'm wearing all the skirts\NI can right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Y'know, Hoshino-san,\NI bet that even with a moustache,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.12,Base,,0,0,0,,you'd {\i1}still {\i0}look pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.84,Base,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh my God. Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.26,Base,,0,0,0,,He didn't. Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.73,Base,,0,0,0,,I've {\i1}never {\i0}gotten called pretty by a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.52,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"We won our first game!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"We won our first game!"\N"Nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.24,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I warmed the bench lmao"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.76,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mere, girls! We've got\Na veteran joining us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:03.00,Base,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! Here's an admittee\Nfrom our dance school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.62,Base,,0,0,0,,second-year Kouka student Yamagishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:09.37,Base,,0,0,0,,She'll be using our studio to practice\Nover her summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:13.72,Base,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:20.98,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're still\Ntrying to get into Kouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this year's my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:27.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. Let me know\Nif I can help you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:32.74,Base,,0,0,0,,You helped me a lot when\NI was trying to get in, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up with Yamagishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's kind of a ditz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:43.54,Base,,0,0,0,,She always went on and on about how\Nshe was gonna be the 'next top star.'
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.96,Base,,0,0,0,,She was good friends with Kaoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.21,Base,,0,0,0,,but then she got in right after\Nninth grade, on her first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow. And Hoshino-san's\Non her fourth try now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.08,Base,,0,0,0,,Guess having connections\Ndoesn't help you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.10,Base,,0,0,0,,You've gotta have the talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.52,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I warmed the bench lmao"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.52,Base,,0,0,0,,"There's a fireworks festival tonight.\NWanna go with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.40,Base,,0,0,0,,My, you're here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Am I coming too often?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:17.77,Base,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I love when\Nyou come to visit me, Kaoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.03,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll be out of the hospital soon, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.46,Base,,0,0,0,,How are your lessons going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:28.09,Base,,0,0,0,,Good. I'm taking eight lessons\Na week right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:31.29,Base,,0,0,0,,My, there aren't even\Nthat many days in the week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:35.98,Base,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful how you young ones\Ncan work so hard and still shine bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:40.77,Base,,0,0,0,,But I worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.16,Base,,0,0,0,,You're such a sweet girl. I don't want you\Nto push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.32,Base,,0,0,0,,If there's something else\Nyou'd like to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.43,Base,,0,0,0,,you're welcome to do that instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.74,Base,,0,0,0,,If there's another life\Nyou'd like to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.44,Base,,0,0,0,,you can always start\Ndown a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:15:59.81,Base,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.01,Base,,0,0,0,,You look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.22,Base,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're not\Ncovering up or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.05,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, the sun's not out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.42,Base,,0,0,0,,This is the first time we've hung out\Nsomewhere other than the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.00,Base,,0,0,0,,You look good in your yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.31,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.76,Base,,0,0,0,,We're gonna miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.52,Base,,0,0,0,,Wanna walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Hungry? We've got piping hot {\i1}okonomiyaki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.65,Base,,0,0,0,,So you're winning all your games!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.02,Base,,0,0,0,,You've won four now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.06,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:49.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.26,Base,,0,0,0,,And it's cool that you're hanging out\Ninstead of practicing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:54.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's got you so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.19,Base,,0,0,0,,I've been doing really well recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.79,Base,,0,0,0,,but I still haven't gotten a chance\Nto play in any games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Makes me wonder, what's the point\Nin trying so hard at baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.45,Base,,0,0,0,,I grew up playing baseball\Nwith my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.51,Base,,0,0,0,,And since my brother's so talented,\Neveryone expects me to be good at it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.79,Base,,0,0,0,,I figured I had to live up\Nto those expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.51,Base,,0,0,0,,so I joined the baseball team\Nwithout a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:32.09,Base,,0,0,0,,But I keep wondering if I'm wasting\Nmy time forcing myself to do all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.72,Base,,0,0,0,,I bet you feel that way\Nall the time, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone always assume that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.16,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't. I never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:54.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure, the pressure gets to me sometimes,\Nbut this is something I {\i1}want {\i0}to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.95,Base,,0,0,0,,I've {\i1}never {\i0}forced myself to do this,\Nnot for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:01.73,Base,,0,0,0,,This is the path I chose! I {\i1}want {\i0}this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.90,Base,,0,0,0,,And I'm not giving up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:08.23,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes\Nto get into the Kouka School!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.33,Base,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:13.17,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't assume I'm like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:13.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.57,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.58,Base,,0,0,0,,For a split second, I felt jealous\Nof the typical high school girl's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:28.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Going to karaoke,\Ngoing on dates, holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:33.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Having a boy worry about me\Nand try to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:49.21,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Falling from the sky ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:54.84,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Like white snow, but warm, ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:19:01.05,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Like a spring fairy ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:06.47,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Fluttering down ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:12.19,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Ah, the Kouka cherry blossoms ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:17.69,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Falling upon the earth,\Nbecoming one with the ground, ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.86,Base,,0,0,0,,--♬ to become new life, and go to you ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.32,Base,,0,0,0,,--I'm going to make it.\N--♬ to become new life, and go to you ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:29.75,Base,,0,0,0,,♬ Now, they flutter and dance ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.50,Base,,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.00,Base,,0,0,0,,I swear I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.63,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Rikuto Tsuji"\N"BLOCK"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:47.76,Base,,0,0,0,,It's between South High and Hama-Dai\Nfor the finals this year again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:51.14,Base,,0,0,0,,South High's down by one in the ninth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:51.35,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"HAMA HIGH: 3"\N"SOUTH HIGH: 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:51.35,Base,,0,0,0,,South High's down by one in the ninth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.64,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"HAMA HIGH: 3"\N"SOUTH HIGH: 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Think they're gonna lose\Nthe final again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:57.32,Base,,0,0,0,,--They still got\Nthe bottom of the ninth...\N--Pinch hitting for\NNumber 9's Shimada-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:02.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Tsuji-kun, Number 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Focus! Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:11.41,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Tsuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:14.62,Base,,0,0,0,,You can do it! Hit it out of the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.85,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! We're missing everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.81,Base,,0,0,0,,It's outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.11,Base,,0,0,0,,--Did they win?\N--That home run clinches the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.94,Base,,0,0,0,,--Yeah, they won! They won!\N--What a way to end a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Whoa, are those tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.86,Base,,0,0,0,,--Aww, you're cryin' tears of joy!\N--South High advances to Koshien!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.37,Base,,0,0,0,,South High went to Koshien but\Nwas eliminated after their first game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.70,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Koshien Stadium"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.70,Base,,0,0,0,,South High went to Koshien but\Nwas eliminated after their first game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.66,Base,,0,0,0,,South High went to Koshien but\Nwas eliminated after their first game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.92,Base,,0,0,0,,My grandma was discharged\Nfrom the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.67,Base,,0,0,0,,and I never went to that bus stop again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.42,Base,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:05.80,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sarasa? Could you {\i1}not{\i0}\Nmake gross noises?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.93,Base,,0,0,0,,You're from Kanagawa, right, Hoshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:13.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about this?\NIt's getting {\i1}tons {\i0}of RTs right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:19.36,Base,,0,0,0,,Someone put this letter up\Nat this bus stop by the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:25.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Please leave this note up for this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:30.45,Base,,0,0,0,,To K: I'm still playing baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows if it's for a boy or a girl,\Nor how old they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Isn't that romantic, though?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:49.05,Base,,0,0,0,,One day, when I walk across\Nthat silver bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.14,Base,,0,0,0,,and you're still playing baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:56.48,Base,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll save you\Na primo seat in the SS section.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.07,Base,,0,0,0,,...that I was in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:29.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}If roses had no thorns and were easier to pick,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:36.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}it would stop being a rose, for it would be a false flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:42.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}Is it the fate of a rose to bloom with thorns?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.91,0:22:46.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}Is it the fate of a person, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}to be born with something predetermined?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:53.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}Could someone tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:23:00.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}The path I walk is already already paved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:07.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}Were the Goddess of Fate by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:13.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}I'd like my path be filled with rainbow-colored flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:20.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.8}Please make that wish of mine come true
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:39.95,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 9: The Two Juliets"
